short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Switch your sessions in an easy way while developing a web application.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Using this extension you can easily switch between different user sessions on the fly for applications that uses the
session-storage field `authenticationToken`.

On the configuration page you can define all your sessions incl. the matching tokens (JWT). Those sessions can then
activated by click on it in the exception popup.

Clear session removes the `authenticationToken` from the session storage and the `JSESSIONID` from the cookies of the
website.
